sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Reader
    participant A as AccessGate
    participant S as Supabase Auth
    participant C as Cipher Module
    participant LS as localStorage
    participant E as Engine (App.jsx)
    participant D as Chapter JSON

    R->>A: Visit companion URL

    Note over A: Step 1 - Identity Authentication
    alt OAuth Provider
        A->>S: signInWithOAuth(google/linkedin)
        S-->>R: Redirect to provider
        R-->>S: Authorize
        S-->>A: Session token + user email
    else Email Magic Link
        A->>S: signInWithOtp(email)
        S-->>R: Magic link email
        Note over A: User can proceed to cipher<br/>while email verifies
    else No Supabase (fallback)
        R->>A: Enter email directly
        A->>A: Store email locally
    end

    Note over A: Step 2 - Book Cipher Authorization
    A->>R: Prompt cipher question<br/>(e.g. "3rd word from page 15")
    R->>A: Enter cipher answer
    A->>C: verifyCipher(answer, validHashes[])
    C->>C: SHA-256(answer.trim().toLowerCase())
    C-->>A: hash match = true/false

    alt Valid Cipher
        A->>LS: Store 30-day access token<br/>{ts, email, provider, verified}
        A->>E: onUnlock(true)
        E->>D: getChapterData(bookId, chapterId)
        D-->>E: {title, sections[]}
        E->>R: Render interactive content
    else Invalid Cipher
        A->>R: "Incorrect. Check your book!"
    end
